      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "+ = Male    - = Female    ? = Unknown\n═══ = Marriage (couple)\n│   = Parent-Child\n┌┴┐ = Siblings\n\nWHY: Symbols let you draw any family fast.\n  + or - fixes gender; ═══ links spouses.\n\nEx: \"A is father of B, B married C\"\n  [+A]\n   │\n  [+B] ═══ [-C]",
