    {
      "id": "el_14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 403,
      "width": 312,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "\"only son of my mother\" = myself(M)\n\"only daughter of my father\" = myself(F)\n\"only child\" = no siblings\n\"only son\" = no brothers\n\"only daughter\" = no sisters\n\nWHY: \"only\" eliminates other siblings.\n  Only son of my mother = I am that son.\n\nEx: \"He is the only son of my mother\"\n  = He is me (speaker is male)\n\nGENDER: he/him/father/son = Male\n        she/her/mother/daughter = Female",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 14,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"only son of my mother\" = myself(M)\n\"only daughter of my father\" = myself(F)\n\"only child\" = no siblings\n\"only son\" = no brothers\n\"only daughter\" = no sisters\n\nWHY: \"only\" eliminates other siblings.\n  Only son of my mother = I am that son.\n\nEx: \"He is the only son of my mother\"\n  = He is me (speaker is male)\n\nGENDER: he/him/father/son = Male\n        she/her/mother/daughter = Female",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
