    {
      "id": "el_25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 782,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Radha's mother = some woman\nStep 2: Husband of that woman = Radha's father\n\n  [+Man] ═══ [-Mother]\n      │\n   [-Radha]\n\nTRICK:\nReplace chain: mother's husband = Father\n(memorize relation shortcuts table)\n\nAnswer: The man is Radha's Father ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
