    {
      "id": "el_33",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1099,
      "width": 801,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "In a coded relation, '+' means 'father of' and '-' means\n'mother of'. If the expression is P + Q - R, how is P\nrelated to R?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 33,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In a coded relation, '+' means 'father of' and '-' means\n'mother of'. If the expression is P + Q - R, how is P\nrelated to R?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_34",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1158,
      "width": 129,
      "height": 17,
      "text": "Solution:",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#7048e8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 34,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1180,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P + Q = P is father of Q\nStep 2: Q - R = Q is mother of R\nStep 3: P(male) -> Q(female) -> R\n\n  [+P] -> [-Q] -> [R]\n\nTRICK:\nCount generations: P is 2 above R\nQ is mother = maternal side\nMale + 2 gen + maternal = maternal grandfather\n\nAnswer: P is maternal grandfather of R ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 35,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P + Q = P is father of Q\nStep 2: Q - R = Q is mother of R\nStep 3: P(male) -> Q(female) -> R\n\n  [+P] -> [-Q] -> [R]\n\nTRICK:\nCount generations: P is 2 above R\nQ is mother = maternal side\nMale + 2 gen + maternal = maternal grandfather\n\nAnswer: P is maternal grandfather of R ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
