    {
      "id": "el_40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1180,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: \"only son of my mother\" = Ravi himself\nStep 2: \"son of Ravi\" = the person in photo\n\n  [-Mother]\n      │\n   [+Ravi]  <- only son = Ravi!\n      │\n   [+Person]\n\nTRICK:\n\"Only son/daughter of my mother/father\"\n= always refers to SELF\nThen read remaining relation from self.\n\nAnswer: Person is Ravi's Son ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
