      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1099,
      "width": 773,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "Mr. and Mrs. Shah have two children: Arti and Sourabh.\nSourabh is married to Ritu, and they have a daughter\nShruti. How is Arti related to Shruti?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
