      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1180,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Mr.Shah + Mrs.Shah -> Arti, Sourabh\nStep 2: Sourabh + Ritu -> Mukti, Shruti\nStep 3: Arti is Sourabh's sister\nStep 4: Shruti's father's sister = Aunt\n\n  [+Mr.Shah] ═══ [-Mrs.Shah]\n  ┌────┴────┐\n[-Arti] [+Sourabh] ═══ [-Ritu]\n             │\n        [-Shruti]\n\nTRICK:\nFather's sister = Bua/Aunt (always)\n\nAnswer: Arti is Aunt of Shruti ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
