    {
      "id": "el_50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1577,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Father's wife = A's mother\nStep 2: Son of A's mother = A's brother\nStep 3: A has no siblings -> must be A!\nStep 4: \"son\" -> B is male\n\n  [+Father] ═══ [-Mother]\n       │\n      [A] <- only child\n\nTRICK:\nNo siblings + parent's child = SELF\nGender from keyword: \"son\" = Male\n\nAnswer: B is A himself ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5000,
      "version": 1,
