      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Father's wife = A's mother\nStep 2: Son of A's mother = A's brother\nStep 3: A has no siblings -> must be A!\nStep 4: \"son\" -> B is male\n\n  [+Father] ═══ [-Mother]\n       │\n      [A] <- only child\n\nTRICK:\nNo siblings + parent's child = SELF\nGender from keyword: \"son\" = Male\n\nAnswer: B is A himself ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
