    {
      "id": "el_55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1577,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A = grandfather(Gen +2)\nStep 2: C = father of B (Gen +1)\nStep 3: D = son of A (Gen +1)\nStep 4: C and D both sons of A\n\n      [+A]       <- Gen +2\n  ┌────┴────┐\n [+C]     [+D]   <- Gen +1\n  │\n [B]             <- Gen 0\n\nTRICK:\nSame parent + same generation = Siblings\n\nAnswer: C and D are Brothers ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
