      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: \"only daughter of my mother\" = Sita\nStep 2: His mother = Sita\nStep 3: Sita is mother of the man\n\n  [-Sita's Mother]\n       │\n    [-Sita]    <- only daughter\n       │\n    [+Man]\n\nTRICK:\n\"only daughter/son of my X\" = myself\nReplace: \"his mother is me\"\n= I am his mother.\n\nAnswer: Sita is the man's Mother ✓",
